                <h2>Cancellation policy </h2>
                <p class="text-justify">According to <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/alitalia-airlines-cancellation-policy.aspx">Alitalia Airlines’ cancellation policy</a>, you can cancel a flight ticket within 24 hours of booking at least 7 days before departure without paying any cancellation fee. However, if you cross the time limitation of 24 hours, you will have to pay the cancellation fee. The charges for cancellation fees depend on the fare type, destination, and the time when you are canceling your tickets. For each ticket you cancel, you will have to pay $30as an administration charge. </p>
                <h3>Refund policy </h3>
                <p class="text-justify">You can cancel a flight ticket within 24 hours of booking without paying any cancellation fee if you completed the purchase 7 days or more before the initially scheduled departure flight. Before you apply for the refund make sure that the ticket is refundable. You will receive the refundable amount after the deduction of the cancelation fee. </p>
                <h4>Frequently asked question</h4>
                <h3 class="text-justify">How to cancel a flight ticket with Alitalia Airlines? </h3>
                <p class="text-justify">You can call the Alitalia Airlines customer care office and inform them about the cancellation. Also, you can visit the official website of the airlines and cancel your flight ticket. </p>
                <h3 class="text-justify">How can I make the request for a refund? By when can I expect it? </h3>
                <p class="text-justify">You can visit the official website of Alitalia Airlines and make a request for a refund or you can call customer care. The airline will process the refund within 7 to 20 business days. </p>
                <h3 class="text-justify">Can I ask for compensation if my flight gets delayed by 2 hours? </h3>
                <p class="text-justify">There can be a possibility that your replacement flight delays your arrival by 2 or more hours or your flight was canceled less than 14 days before departure, you are eligible to get compensation. </p>
                <h3 class="text-justify">How to check if my flight is refundable? </h3>
